# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:40
translate spanish hwb_s07_069eb79d:

    # Marina "It sure was nice for Mariah and her friends to let us use some of their equipment."
    Marina "Было так мило со стороны Марии и ее друзей одолжить нам некоторое оборудование."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:46
translate spanish hwb_s07_246a8720:

    # Amber "Only after that Joseph guy begged her to."
    Amber "Сразу после того, как тот парень, Джозеф, начал умолять ее сделать это."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:50
translate spanish hwb_s07_03239880:

    # "I pause to look around. We decided to wait until nightfall to go look around some more."
    "Me detengo para mirar alrededor. Decidimos esperar hasta el anochecer para seguir explorando."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:52
translate spanish hwb_s07_9d485cd1:

    # "It’s like an entirely different world the further you get from the insanity. Quiet and calm, the only lights are the stars and the faint glow of the campground, the campers and motorhomes flickering in the distance."
    "Es como un mundo completamente diferente cuanto más te alejas del caos. Tranquilo y calmado, las únicas luces son las estrellas y el tenue resplandor del campamento, las casas rodantes y autocaravanas parpadeando a lo lejos."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:60
translate spanish hwb_s07_4e0662b8:

    # "Marina fiddles with the metal detector’s headphones, removing them halfway."
    "Marina juega con los auriculares del detector de metales, quitándoselos a medias."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:62
translate spanish hwb_s07_6ffb439b:

    # Marina "Sorry, the beeping's loud. What was that?"
    Marina "Прости, писк слишком громкий. Что ты сказала?"

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:67
translate spanish hwb_s07_60001fae:

    # Amber "Forget it. I’m not playing that game. Just keep listening."
    Amber "Забей. Не важно. Просто продолжай слушать."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:71
translate spanish hwb_s07_350456c8:

    # Marina "Oh!"
    Marina "Ой!"

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:73
translate spanish hwb_s07_599a5fbb:

    # Amber "Did you find something?"
    Amber "Нашла что-то?"

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:77
translate spanish hwb_s07_e7f9da49:

    # Marina "I think so! It’s over here!"
    Marina "Думаю да! Вот здесь!"

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:82
translate spanish hwb_s07_23c4a465:

    # "I set aside my shovel and throw myself to the ground, clawing at the sand."
    "Dejo a un lado mi pala y me lanzo al suelo, escarbando la arena con las manos."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:84
translate spanish hwb_s07_84230b33:

    # "A shiny speck sticks out of the ground. Frantically, I dig it up."
    "Una mota brillante sobresale del suelo. Frenéticamente, la desentierro."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:88
translate spanish hwb_s07_e6396c5a:

    # Marina "Is it the gold?"
    Marina "Это золото?"

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:90
translate spanish hwb_s07_e3d411aa:

    # Amber "It’s—!"
    Amber "Это—!"

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:92
translate spanish hwb_s07_91225657:

    # "I scrape harder."
    "Raspo con más fuerza."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:94
translate spanish hwb_s07_e3d411aa_1:

    # Amber "It’s—!"
    Amber "Это—!"

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:96
translate spanish hwb_s07_ecd28f4b:

    # "Harder."
    "Más fuerte."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:98
translate spanish hwb_s07_ad309f5c:

    # Amber "It’s—"
    Amber "Это—"

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:103
translate spanish hwb_s07_9a389c2e:

    # "Finally, I unearth it and hold it up to the starlight."
    "Finalmente, la desentierro y la levanto hacia la luz de las estrellas."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:108
translate spanish hwb_s07_019f6326:

    # Amber "—a soda tab."
    Amber "—ушко от банки с газировкой."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:112
translate spanish hwb_s07_f4feef2a:

    # Amber "Dammit! This is the fifth one!"
    Amber "Черт! Это уже пятое!"

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:116
translate spanish hwb_s07_2863b3dd:

    # Marina "If we find anymore, we could start making a curtain out of them!"
    Marina "Если найдем еще хоть одну, можем начать делать из них занавески!"

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:120
translate spanish hwb_s07_fd2b7270:

    # "I send the tab flying, speeding off over the dikes."
    "Lanzo la anilla volando, alejándose sobre los diques."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:124
translate spanish hwb_s07_4b1137f5:

    # Marina "Maybe we should call it a night. I'm sure we can find it once we're fresh in the morning."
    Marina "Может, нам лучше закончить на сегодня. Уверена, что у нас больше шансов найти его утром на свежую голову."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:128
translate spanish hwb_s07_41d016b4:

    # Amber "Nah, that’s no good. We can only do it now because Parks and Recreation isn’t paying as much attention."
    Amber "Неа, так не пойдет. Нам надо это сделать именно сейчас, пока охрана Парков и Зоны отдыха не обращает на нас внимания."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:133
translate spanish hwb_s07_67fa8584:

    # Marina "Why would they ever pay attention? That show stopped airing months ago."
    Marina "А с чего бы им вообще обращать внимание? Тот сериал перестал выходить в эфир еще несколько месяцев назад."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:143
translate spanish hwb_s07_ed9b4a17:

    # "Though even now, someone’s still guarding the area near the campground."
    "Aunque incluso ahora, alguien sigue vigilando el área cerca del campamento."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:145
translate spanish hwb_s07_7e9cb5fa:

    # "The rocks give us some cover, so I don’t think we’ll be spotted, but we still need to be careful."
    "Las rocas nos dan algo de cobertura, así que no creo que nos vean, pero aún debemos tener cuidado."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:147
translate spanish hwb_s07_7249f760:

    # Amber "We’ll keep looking for a little while. If we can’t find anything, we might want to assume the worst."
    Amber "Мы еще немного поищем. Если мы не сможем ничего найти, то нам, вероятно, придется признать самое худшее."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:151
translate spanish hwb_s07_8e4dd5a7:

    # "Her face wrenches with hopelessness."
    "Su rostro se retuerce de desesperanza."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:153
translate spanish hwb_s07_0ad92521:

    # Marina "That somebody else found it?"
    Marina "То, что его нашел кто-то другой?"

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:157
translate spanish hwb_s07_44884238:

    # Amber "That it doesn’t exist!"
    Amber "То, что его не существует!"

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:161
translate spanish hwb_s07_38bf9b79:

    # Amber "Geez, it’s like you’ve never even considered that it might not be real."
    Amber "Блин, да брось, будто бы ты ни разу не предполагала у себя в мыслях, что его попросту нет."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:165
translate spanish hwb_s07_6457a3d4:

    # Marina "But Mariah—"
    Marina "Но Мария—"

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:169
translate spanish hwb_s07_cdd858ae:

    # Amber "Yeah, yeah. I know."
    Amber "Да, да. Я знаю."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:175
translate spanish hwb_s07_d8334b92:

    # "I grab my shovel and swing it back over my shoulder. As we walk, we stay as close to the mountain range as possible."
    "Agarro mi pala y la balanceo sobre mi hombro. Mientras caminamos, nos mantenemos lo más cerca posible de la cadena montañosa."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:179
translate spanish hwb_s07_a3f28f74:

    # Amber "Why are you so gung-ho about this thing, anyway?"
    Amber "Почему ты так помешана на этом сокровище?"

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:183
translate spanish hwb_s07_30136696:

    # Amber "If you’re just in it for the cash, there are better ways to make money than dragging yourself around the desert."
    Amber "Если ты ввязалась в это только из-за денег, то есть способы и получше достать их, чем шляться по пустыне."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:189
translate spanish hwb_s07_a04dc7e1:

    # Marina "Oh no, it’s nothing like that!"
    Marina "О нет, дело совсем не в этом!"

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:193
translate spanish hwb_s07_6324fbd7:

    # Marina "It’s just…"
    Marina "Просто…"

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:195
translate spanish hwb_s07_93d889bd:

    # "Her voice trails off. It hangs over us, never fully evaporating into the cool night air."
    "Su voz se desvanece. Se cierne sobre nosotras, sin evaporarse nunca por completo en el aire fresco de la noche."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:199
translate spanish hwb_s07_0a78284c:

    # Amber "It’s okay. Don’t feel like you have to tell me."
    Amber "Все нормально. Ты не обязана мне объяснять."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:201
translate spanish hwb_s07_c6e01cbd:

    # "We both have things we don’t want to talk about. That’s becoming very clear."
    "Ambas tenemos cosas de las que no queremos hablar. Eso se está volviendo muy claro."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:203
translate spanish hwb_s07_bce0e361:

    # "At least Marina doesn’t swerve off the road so she can go pout."
    "Al menos Marina no se desvía del camino para ir a hacer pucheros."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:207
translate spanish hwb_s07_baf1e22f:

    # "I just don’t want to think about it. All I’ve been doing for the last month is thinking about it. I almost wish my brain would quit working so I wouldn’t have to."
    "Simplemente no quiero pensar en eso. Todo lo que he hecho durante el último mes es pensar en ello. Casi desearía que mi cerebro dejara de funcionar para no tener que hacerlo."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:209
translate spanish hwb_s07_72b68513:

    # "So naturally, I take a long, lonely trip, with nothing to do except think."
    "Así que, naturalmente, hago un viaje largo y solitario, sin nada que hacer excepto pensar."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:213
translate spanish hwb_s07_9facec45:

    # Marina "Amber, it’s happening again!"
    Marina "Эмбер, тут еще кое-что!"

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:215
translate spanish hwb_s07_f726d4b5:

    # "Marina stops, hands quivering as she tightens her grip."
    "Marina se detiene, las manos temblorosas mientras aprieta el agarre."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:219
translate spanish hwb_s07_0f084d0e:

    # Amber "I swear, if this is another soda tab…"
    Amber "Я клянусь, если это еще одно ушко…"

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:223
translate spanish hwb_s07_c5612cc6:

    # Marina "I don’t think it is. The beeping is really loud, and it’s vibrating a lot."
    Marina "Не думаю. Пищит действительно громко и сильно вибрирует."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:227
translate spanish hwb_s07_7fc584bd:

    # Amber "Wait. It’s vibrating?"
    Amber "Подожди. Вибрирует?"

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:229
translate spanish hwb_s07_b1db4544:

    # Marina "Uh-huh. It feels weird."
    Marina "Ага. Это странно."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:233
translate spanish hwb_s07_c4bfaf0d:

    # Amber "That's not the only weird feeling thing that's going to be vibrating."
    Amber "Это не единственная кажущаяся странной вещь, которая будет вибрировать."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:237
translate spanish hwb_s07_8b6aa3cb:

    # "The metal detector hovers over the ground between the rock and the sand. I thrust my shovel into the spot, the metal scraping against the edge of the dike."
    "El detector de metales se cierne sobre el suelo entre la roca y la arena. Clavo mi pala en el lugar, el metal raspando contra el borde del dique."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:239
translate spanish hwb_s07_cd625b30:

    # "Planting my foot the shovel’s head, I drive it further into the ground, using every ounce of my strength to dig."
    "Plantando mi pie en la cabeza de la pala, la hundo más en la tierra, usando cada gramo de mi fuerza para cavar."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:241
translate spanish hwb_s07_b0b6f36f:

    # "The first load of dirt and sand unclenches from the ground, loosening the earth around it."
    "La primera palada de tierra y arena se desprende del suelo, aflojando la tierra a su alrededor."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:243
translate spanish hwb_s07_265c5072:

    # "I throw the load aside and repeat the process. Each time, it’s a little easier, a little lighter."
    "Arrojo la palada a un lado y repito el proceso. Cada vez, es un poco más fácil, un poco más ligero."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:249
translate spanish hwb_s07_77f44e84:

    # "Finally, the shovel strikes something hard, sending a shocking vibration through my hand and up my entire body."
    "Finalmente, la pala golpea algo duro, enviando una vibración impactante a través de mi mano y por todo mi cuerpo."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:253
translate spanish hwb_s07_6fc0d91a:

    # Marina "Bedrock?"
    Marina "Коренная порода?"

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:255
translate spanish hwb_s07_ae729311:

    # Amber "I haven’t dug that deep."
    Amber "Я не копала так глубоко."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:260
translate spanish hwb_s07_a21bdfed:

    # "Dropping to my knees, I reach my hands into the hole and brush off the remaining dirt."
    "Cayendo de rodillas, meto las manos en el hoyo y limpio la tierra restante."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:266
translate spanish hwb_s07_d7e9c61d:

    # "Marina leans in. The sound of her anxiously swallowing is barely audible over my heavy breathing."
    "Marina se inclina. El sonido de su trago nervioso apenas se escucha sobre mi respiración agitada."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:282
translate spanish hwb_s07_e76e050b:

    # "My fingers brush against something. I gulp and pull out the hole’s contents—a small, rotting wood box."
    "Mis dedos rozan algo. Trago saliva y saco el contenido del hoyo: una pequeña caja de madera podrida."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:286
translate spanish hwb_s07_e046ad36:

    # "My heart stops."
    "Mi corazón se detiene."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:288
translate spanish hwb_s07_86898dc2:

    # "Trembling, I open the box, the leftover dirt falling into my lap."
    "Temblando, abro la caja, y la tierra sobrante cae en mi regazo."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:290
translate spanish hwb_s07_72e3b89c:

    # "Gold."
    "Oro."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:294
translate spanish hwb_s07_09779fe2:

    # Amber "{cps=80}I-{w=0.3}It{/cps}{cps=3}... {w=0.3}{/cps}{cps=80}It exists?{/cps}"
    Amber "{cps=80}О-{w=0.3}оно{/cps}{cps=3}... {w=0.3}{/cps}{cps=80}Оно существует?{/cps}"

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:296
translate spanish hwb_s07_f92bda14:

    # Amber "It exists?!"
    Amber "Оно правда существует?!"

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:300
translate spanish hwb_s07_8d2eb8a4:

    # Marina "{size=+10}IT EXISTS!{/size}"
    Marina "{size=+10}ОНО СУЩЕСТВУЕТ!{/size}"

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:304
translate spanish hwb_s07_b905cb7e:

    # "Marina yells at the top of her lungs, a yell so loud that it bounces off the mountain, echoing off to the horizon and then back again."
    "Marina grita a todo pulmón, un grito tan fuerte que rebota en la montaña, haciendo eco hasta el horizonte y luego de vuelta."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:306
translate spanish hwb_s07_f57d9254:

    # "Marina has been unleashed."
    "Marina se ha desatado."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:308
translate spanish hwb_s07_2f47a37f:

    # Amber "Not so loud, they might hear us."
    Amber "Не так громко, они могут нас услышать."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:310
translate spanish hwb_s07_3c239099:

    # "She lowers her voice to an excited whisper, channeling her energy into bouncing up and down."
    "Baja la voz a un susurro emocionado, canalizando su energía en saltos de alegría."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:312
translate spanish hwb_s07_a1c2219b:

    # Marina "But it exists! I told you it did!"
    Marina "Но оно существует! Я говорила тебе, что оно существует!"

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:314
translate spanish hwb_s07_92503546:

    # "She’s right, and despite being proven wrong, I can’t help but smile."
    "Tiene razón, y a pesar de haber sido refutado, no puedo evitar sonreír."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:316
translate spanish hwb_s07_9f1c99c8:

    # "Here I thought it was gonna be some plastic treasure chest with a coupon for chocolate milk inside it or something equally shameless and corporate."
    "Y yo que pensaba que sería un cofre de tesoro de plástico con un cupón para leche con chocolate adentro o algo igualmente descarado y corporativo."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:322
translate spanish hwb_s07_43944b9e:

    # Marina "Ambeeeeer!"
    Marina "Эмбеееер!"

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:324
translate spanish hwb_s07_0c155011:

    # "My only warning is a quick gust of wind."
    "Mi única advertencia es una rápida ráfaga de viento."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:326
translate spanish hwb_s07_f9484075:

    # "Before I even have a chance to brace for it, I’m engulfed by Marina and her hug."
    "Antes de que siquiera tenga tiempo de prepararme, soy envuelta por Marina y su abrazo."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:328
translate spanish hwb_s07_35eb8af2:

    # Amber "Wh-{w=0.6}What?"
    Amber "Чт-{w=0.6}Что?"

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:330
translate spanish hwb_s07_fadc1e63:

    # Marina "It’s real! I told you it was! I told you!"
    Marina "Оно существует! Я же говорила! Я говорила!"

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:332
translate spanish hwb_s07_af5a64de:

    # "I stop for a second, then smile."
    "Me detengo un segundo, luego sonrío."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:334
translate spanish hwb_s07_58079675:

    # Amber "Yeah. You were right. It’s real."
    Amber "Ага. Ты была права. Оно существует."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:336
translate spanish hwb_s07_267f4a2f:

    # Marina "Should we tell someone? What do we even do now?"
    Marina "Должны ли мы рассказать об этом кому-то? Что нам вообще теперь делать?"

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:338
translate spanish hwb_s07_7a6b1ff4:

    # Amber "Honestly?"
    Amber "Честно?"

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:340
translate spanish hwb_s07_cc7d88d5:

    # Amber "I’m not sure."
    Amber "Я не уверена."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:342
translate spanish hwb_s07_180ad3d9:

    # Amber "It’s getting pretty late, though. Let’s pack it up for the night. We can think about what to do in the morning."
    Amber "Тем не менее, уже довольно поздно. Давай ночью передохнем. Мы можем утром подумать о том, что делать дальше."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:344
translate spanish hwb_s07_94cf3f46:

    # "For now, we can just marvel at the fact that it’s not bogus."
    "Por ahora, podemos maravillarnos del hecho de que no es una farsa."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:346
translate spanish hwb_s07_56bae92a:

    # Amber "Sound like a plan?"
    Amber "Звучит как план?"

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:348
translate spanish hwb_s07_9f0b0c96:

    # Marina "It does, but…"
    Marina "Да, но…"

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:352
translate spanish hwb_s07_793136cc:

    # "She takes a deep, long breath, inhaling all the air around and maybe even some of mine, then releases it all at once."
    "Toma una respiración larga y profunda, inhalando todo el aire a su alrededor y quizás un poco del mío, luego lo suelta todo de una vez."

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:354
translate spanish hwb_s07_d9612e43:

    # Marina "{size=+10}IT’S ACTUALLY REALLY REAL!{/size}"
    Marina "{size=+10}ОНО ПО-НАСТОЯЩЕМУ ДЕЙСТВИТЕЛЬНО СУЩЕСТВУЕТ!{/size}"

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:356
translate spanish hwb_s07_12b50039:

    # Amber "Marina, quiet! They’re gonna hear us!"
    Amber "Марина, тише! Они услышат нас!"

# game/script/hwb_s07.rpy:239
translate spanish hwb_s07_4705152c:

    # "Planting my foot on the shovel’s head, I drive it further into the ground, using every ounce of my strength to dig."
    "Plantando mi pie en la cabeza de la pala, la hundo más en la tierra, usando cada gramo de mi fuerza para cavar."

translate spanish strings:

    # script/hwb_s07.rpy:375
    old "Walking back to the RV"
    new "Walking back to the RV"

